title: McIlvoy Minute: Sam Houston St., SFA set for 90th meeting
text:
Tweet HOUSTON - 
There are College Football Rivalries and then there is the Battle of the Piney Woods. For the historians out there, this weekend will mark the 90th meeting between the Bearkats and Lumberjacks and as they've done for several years, they will meet inside of NRG Stadium. 
Sam Houston State comes in 1-2 including a close loss to Texas Tech to open the season while SFA has struggled with injuries and is 0-4 but ready to breakthrough with a victory. 
The Bearkats come in winning the last 4 and 9 out of the last 11 meetings. Quick Clicks
